OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779930189
OL,3,CEnergy bills to rise by more than #200
OL,4,Cper year as Iran war impacts households
OL,6,FHousehold energy bills will rise by
OL,7,Fmore than #200 a year for average
OL,8,Fhouseholds from July after the energy
OL,9,Fprice cap was increased on Wednesday
OL,10,Fmorning.
OL,12,FThe 13% rise announced by energy
OL,13,Fregulator Ofgem sets the maximum price
OL,14,Fper unit of gas and electricity used
OL,15,Ffrom July to September for a typical
OL,16,Fdual fuel household across England,
OL,17,FScotland and Wales.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
