CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779930189
OL,3,CEnergy bills to rise by more than #200
OL,4,Cper year as Iran war impacts households
OL,6,FFor these households, energy bills
OL,7,Fwill rise by #209 a year to #1,850
OL,8,Ffrom July 1 ` an increase of 13% on
OL,9,FApril's #1,641 annual cap.
OL,11,FIt marks the first price cap set since
OL,12,Fthe start of the Iran war on February
OL,13,F28, which triggered a blockade of the
OL,14,Fcrucial Strait of Hormuz shipping
OL,15,Froute and led to significant
OL,16,Fdisruption of trade and global energy
OL,17,Fmarkets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779930189
OL,3,CEnergy bills to rise by more than #200
OL,4,Cper year as Iran war impacts households
OL,6,FHouseholds have yet to feel the impact
OL,7,Fon their energy bills, as the price
OL,8,Fcap is reviewed on a quarterly basis,
OL,9,Fand April saw a 7% drop thanks to
OL,10,Fgovernment measures to reduce bills.
OL,12,FWith the new cap set, households will
OL,13,Fbe largely shielded over the warm
OL,14,Fsummer months, but concerns are
OL,15,Fgrowing over a painful hit when the
OL,16,Fcap is reviewed in October, and energy
OL,17,Fdemand rises as temperatures drop.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779930189
OL,3,CEnergy bills to rise by more than #200
OL,4,Cper year as Iran war impacts households
OL,6,FEnergy market analysts Cornwall
OL,7,FInsight suggest the cap in October
OL,8,Fwill be at a similar level to July,
OL,9,Feven if the Middle East conflict were
OL,10,Fto end soon, due to the physical
OL,11,Fdamage to infrastructure and the
OL,12,Flingering effect of disrupted supply.
OL,14,FCalls have been mounting for the
OL,15,Fgovernment to set out action to
OL,16,Fsupport the most vulnerable, but
OL,17,FChancellor Rachel Reeves stopped short
OL,18,Fof any immediate energy measures in
OL,19,Fher cost-of-living plan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
