OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779930189
OL,3,CEnergy bills to rise by more than #200
OL,4,Cper year as Iran war impacts households
OL,6,FShe told MPs last week: "We stand
OL,7,Fready to act if market conditions
OL,8,Fworsen significantly later this year
OL,9,Fand I have been leading cross-
OL,10,Fgovernment contingency work on design
OL,11,Fof potential future targeted and
OL,12,Ftemporary support for businesses."
OL,14,FCampaigners have warned of an
OL,15,F"extremely difficult winter" ahead for
OL,16,Fthe most vulnerable without extra
OL,17,Fsupport on bills.
OL,26,@nD@YOUtD@bO]wD@AOUwD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
