OL,3,CEnergy bills to rise by more than #200
OL,4,Cper year as Iran war impacts households
OL,6,FSimon Francis, co-ordinator of the End
OL,7,FFuel Poverty Coalition, said:
OL,8,F"Households need reassurance and
OL,9,Fsupport, not a summer of suspense.
OL,11,F"That means the government must act
OL,12,Fbefore winter to spell out what
OL,13,Fsupport will be available."
OL,15,FThe government has insisted that
OL,16,F"tackling the affordability crisis is
OL,17,Four number one priority".
OL,26,@pD@AOUsD@AOUuD@[O]xD@AOUyD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
