OL,3,CEnergy bills to rise by more than #200
OL,4,Cper year as Iran war impacts households
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIts package of support measures so far
OL,12,Fincludes a cut in the rate of VAT on
OL,13,Fattraction tickets over the summer
OL,14,Fholidays, free bus travel for children
OL,15,Fin England during August, extending
OL,16,Fthe 5p-per-litre fuel duty reduction
OL,17,Fand lowering import tariffs on more
OL,18,Fthan 100 types of food products.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
